import
------
- profile download vs. unescaping to speed up retrieval
    - on a 33 KB image download takes less than 1s over 100 MBit ethernet
    - unescaping takes 14s on a 266 MHz Mobile Pentium MMX with 64 MB RAM
    - nothing much can be done about this at present, I guess
    - even unescaping in memory it takes _way_ longer than the download
    - guess we'll have to wait for binary safe transfer
    - or perhaps use a binary cursor ?

- investigate binary cursors

- move/remove succesfully imported files
    - make this an option

